    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, complemented by a suspension system that retains its factory-intended kinematic precision. A well-sorted example ideal for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and dyanmic feedback.",
