      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality, having been maintained with a detail-oriented eye. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant luster, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show light bolstering wear but remain firm and comfortable, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have kept a comprehensive log of all oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It recently passed a full safety inspection and is fitted with high-quality tires that have plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
